# Phase 7 — Build Log

**Goal:** Conviction layer. Make every tool page feel full, personalize Find My Stack, and frame each plan card as "yes, this is your pick."

**Design decisions (locked via brainstorm on 2026-04-12):**
- A: Sentiment block on tool page, placed after "Our Views"; auto-generate on tools with ≥10 views, CTA fallback otherwise
- B: 6-field intake modal appearing after query submit; fields = skill, budget, team, industry, goal type, existing tools; localStorage persistence
- C: Match score (deterministic) + batched Claude call for "why for you" rationale (zero net new API calls)

See [`../plan.md`](../plan.md) for the full spec.

